title: NFTs, the metaverse and the future of digital art | Elizabeth Strickler
itunes:author: Elizabeth Strickler
description: In need of a brief yet illuminating lesson on the obsession with NFTs? Elizabeth Strickler breaks down the acronym and explains the fundamentals of non-fungible tokens, sharing how these digital assets are changing the landscape for artists and content creators looking to cash in on their creations -- in and out of the metaverse.
